description.narrative: Increased contribution to achieving regional Key Results for Children through more systematic community engagement (CE) approaches, behaviors and social norms research and programming, and demand generation. The strive to improve the quality of C4D programming has created a strong momentum for enhancing the focus on positives social change in the region, with the alignment of the regional vision for the acceleration of KRCs (cultural and social drivers identified as one key accelerator) and the growing understanding, interest and demand from COs for support in social change programming, harmonization and integration of community engagement approaches. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:31/12/2019
